quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  20,126,"Alla O Toowii O Daala jaabagol mo: "Ko yeru ﾉ蓉n golluﾉ預a ka aduna, gomﾉ擁i ariino e maaﾉ預 Aayeeje Amen ﾉ容n ﾉ蓉rniﾉ預a e majje ﾉ預luﾉ預a ﾉ容, ko wano nii, pellet, an hannde a ﾉ預lete ka nder Lepte"."
  20,127,"Ko yeru ndii njoﾉ電i Men yoﾉ殿ta on mutuﾉ擁 e welnuruuji harminaaﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n, o ﾉ蓉rnii e gomﾉ擁nal ngal wonndude e daliilaaji ﾉ殿nnguﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n ka Joomi makko. Pellet, ko Lepte Alla ﾉ容n ka Laakara ﾉ砥ri ﾉ容nﾆｴinnde ko ﾉ容n kadi ﾉ砥ri dolnude diini ngurndam ﾉ妬ttuﾉ預m ﾉ預m ka aduna e ka Barjakhu ko ﾉ容n kadi ﾉ砥rata duumaade."
  20,128,"Kaa hara ﾉ殿nnganaali sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n heewugol moftaaji ﾉ擁 Men halki ﾉ蓉m ado maﾉ橡兎, hiﾉ兎 yaha e koﾉ熔oli ﾉ擁n moftaaji halkanooﾉ擁, ﾉ兎 yi'a batteeji ko heﾉ妬ﾉ兎 kon? Pellet, ko heﾉ妬 kon ﾉ擁n moftaaji ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ﾉ擁 immorde e halkeede e yirbineede ﾉ蓉m ko tasakuyee wonannde joomiraaﾉ兎 hakkillaaji ﾉ兎n."
  20,129,"Hara wonaano Daalol adii ngol immorde ka Joomi maaﾉ預 -an Nulaaﾉ熔- Kanko o Leptataa hay e gooto ko adii O darnude hujja e hoore makko, hara wanaano lajal hoddiraangal ﾉ兎 ka Makko O yaccinanayno ﾉ兎 Lepteﾉ容n; sabu hanndugol maﾉ橡兎 e majje."
  20,130,"Munﾃｱo -an Nulaaﾉ熔- e dow ko fennooﾉ兎 ma ﾉ兎n wowlata kon immorde e sifaaji meerenteeji, subuhino yettaa Joomi maaﾉ預 ka Julde Subaka ko adii ﾆｴellitagol naange ngen, e ka Julde Alansaraa ko adii mutugol magge, e ka Julde Futuroo e Gee- ﾆｴe immorde e saa'iiji jemma on, e ka Julde Fanaa ka mortagol magge ﾉ殿awo lannugol feccere arane- re nden ka ﾃｱallal e ka Julde Futuroo ﾉ殿awo lannugol feccere ﾉ擁ﾉ預ﾉ兎re nden e ﾃｱallal ngal; jorto fii yo a heﾉ砥 ka Alla immorde e mbarjaari ko waltortaa ﾉ蓉m."
  20,131,"Wata a ndaaru faade e ko Men waﾉ預ni kon nooneeji ﾉ兎e fennuﾉ兎 dakamme hiﾉ兎 dakmitora mo immorde e cuﾉ預ari ngurndan aduna fii yo Men ndarndo ﾉ兎, anndu pellet, koo ko Men waﾉ預niﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉m ko iwayﾉ蓉m, Mbarjaari Joomi maa ndi O Fodumaa ndin a heﾉ殿y haaweltoﾉ預a ko ndin ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴude diini ko Men dakmiti ﾉ兎 kon ka aduna immorde dakkamme iwoowo e ﾉ砥roowo duumaade; sabu kanko o taﾆｴataa."
  20,132,"Yamir -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ﾆ‘ynguure maa nden tottugol Julde nden, munﾃｱitoraa an kadi e dow tottugol nde, Men ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬raali ma arsikugol wonkii maa wanaa tanaa maaﾉ預 kadi, Menen Meﾉ容n Fawtii arsike maa on, battane moﾆｴﾆｴe ﾉ容n ka aduna e ka Laakara wonanii joomiraaﾉ兎 kulol Alla ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎n hulooﾉ兎 Mo ﾉ兎 ﾉ熔ftoo Yamiraaﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ容n, ﾉ兎 woﾉ遼擁too kadi haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n."
  20,133,"ﾆ‘e heeferﾉ兎 fennuﾉ兎 Annabiijo (yo Alla juulu e makko hisina) wi'i: "Ko haﾉ擁 Muhammadu addana men maande ka Joomi makko nde no tinndina e goongungol makko ko o Nulaaﾉ熔?" Enee, hara araali e ﾉ兎e fennuﾉ兎 ndee Alqur'aanaare, nden tawnde ko kayre woni goonginnde Defte kammu yankeeje ﾉ容n ado mayre?!"
  20,134,"Sinndo Menen Men halkirno ﾉ兎e fennuﾉ兎 Annabiijo (yo Alla juulu e makko hisina) jippinngol Lepte e maﾉ橡兎 sabu geddi maﾉ橡兎 e sannalﾉ預aku maﾉ橡兎 ko adii Men Nulude e maﾉ橡兎 Nulaaﾉ兎, Men jippina e maﾉ橡兎 Deftere, ﾉ兎 wi'ayno ﾃ疎lnde Darngal ko ﾉ兎 ngantiniiﾉ兎 gaayi keefeeraaku maﾉ橡兎: "Joomi amen ko hannoo Nulaa e amen Nulaaﾉ熔 ka aduna, men gomﾉ擁nira sabu makko men jokka ko o addi kon immorde e Aayeeje ko adii hoyre nden e hersa kan jipporde e amen sabu Lepte Maa ﾉ容n."
  20,135,"Maakan -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ﾉ兎e fennuﾉ兎: "Gooto kala e amen e onon no habbitii ko Alla yoﾉ殿ta kon, onon kadi habbitee, on anndoyay -feere woo alaa- ko hommbo woni jom Laawol Focciingol ngol, ko homﾉ兎 woni feewuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n: Ko menen kaa ko onon?"